To the Parent/Guardian(s) of Pennfield Area Students;

The Meet Up and Eat Up student meals program is still open and operating. The Governor's Executive Order related to the Stay-Home-Stay-Safe announcement allows the Meet Up and Eat Up student meals program to continue serving our area students.

Be Safe and Be Well

